How to run testcase framework:-
Install these command(linux):-

1. install node.js
2. sudo apt-get install curl python-software-properties
   curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_10.x | sudo -E bash -
   sudo apt-get install nodejs
3. npm install -g testcafe
4. apt-get install xvfb

Can create test file using extension:-
1. .js

give premission to read write and execute:- chmod +x filename.js

Command to run the test case :-

xvfb-run --server-num=99 --server-args='-ac -screen 0 1024x768x16' testcafe firefox path/filename.js





